    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Hey there! Looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for its next big adventure? I\u2019m parting with my trusty car, and it\u2019s in really wonderful shape! It\u2019s been well-loved and runs like a dream, making it perfect for daily commutes or weekend getaways. It\u2019s got plenty of life left in it and looks sharp inside and out. Come take it for a spin\u2014I\u2019m sure you\u2019ll love it as much as I have!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
