    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring a 11.5:1 compression ratio and individual throttle bodies for instantaneous throttle response. The high-pressure double VANOS system has been serviced, ensuring optimal cam phasing across the power band. Power is delivered through a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M differential lock. Crucially, this chassis has received rear subframe reinforcement and rod bearing replacement\u2014essential preventative measures for this platform. The suspension retains its factory-spec damping characteristics with no sign of bushing deflection, providing the communicative steering feel and lateral stability expected of an M-division product. A mechanically sound driver's car that prioritizes performance over concours-level aesthetics.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 22
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Clean title. Well-maintained engine. Reliable daily driver.",
      "price": 31500.0,
