    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a remarkably well-maintained vehicle that strikes the ideal balance between everyday utility and premium comfort. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like finish, though a discerning eye will notice a few minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small, superficial scratch near the trunk lid\u2014standard signs of careful road use. Step inside to a pristine, non-smoker cabin where the leather upholstery remains soft and supportive, showing only light natural creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster. Every feature, from the premium sound system to the heated seats and navigation, is in perfect working order. Under the hood, the engine runs quietly and delivers smooth, responsive power, backed by a comprehensive service log. We recently completed a full fluid flush and multi-point inspection to ensure it is road-trip ready. The tires are at roughly 70% tread, and the brakes feel firm and confident. This is a transparently represented, solid vehicle looking for its next long-term home.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
