    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b I'm looking for a new home for my trusty ride! It's been such a reliable companion and is still in really wonderful shape. It drives like a dream and definitely has plenty of adventures left in it. I've taken great care of it, and I'm sure you're going to love it just as much as I have! Perfect for anyone looking for a solid, dependable vehicle. Let's get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 29500.0,
