    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sorted 2011 BMW M3 featuring the iconic S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This high-revving powerplant, characterized by its eight individual throttle bodies and 8,400 RPM redline, is paired with a tactile 6-speed manual transmission. The vehicle retains its sharp handling dynamics thanks to M-specific aluminum suspension geometry and a functional M Variable Differential Lock. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rod bearing replacement and updated throttle actuators, ensuring the valvetrain and VANOS system perform optimally. While the aesthetics reflect honest road use, the chassis and drivetrain integrity remain high, offering the communicative hydraulic steering and linear power delivery synonymous with the E9x platform.",
